ComicInfo.Summary:
Things heat up as Ember hires the Lookers to find out who hacked a delicate video from her. But Tanya and Michelle find it has turned into something much deeper they stumble into one cover-up over the next. From webcam girls to super spies, this will be a crazy ride from writer Pat Shand and artist Gabriel Andrade! But this ongoing series gets better - each issue has an Ember solo story as well, written and drawn by Christian Zanier!
